data.description: Awesome Brick Home, Custom Built Tri-Level located close to schools, shopping, major highways & minutes away from Lake Michigan, sitting on a 0.31 Acre lot. This home interior features over 2.340 square feet, above average room sizes, the living rm. w wood burning stone fireplace, bay window with hardwood floors, formal dining rm eat in kitchen, laundry rm. & half bath on the main level. Step up to the awesome master suite w private bath & walk in closet plus 2 other generous bedrooms & a 2nd full bath on the 2nd level. Step down to the finished basement that is all set for you to entertain your guests as it includes a family room with a 2nd brick fireplace! If you step out of the dining room to the large wood deck you will appreciate the beauty scenery of the sprawling 0.31-acre lot. Whenever you come home and pull into the attached 2 car garage you can take a deep breath and enjoy all the other features too numerous to mention.  This perfect combination is of country setting in the city is so hard to find so don't hesitate to request your private tour. You will be impressed the moment you step foot into this home awaiting you to move right in!
